  <brief_title>Clopidogrel as Adjunctive Reperfusion Therapy - Thrombolysis in Myocardial Infarction</brief_title>
  <acronym>CLARITY-TIMI28</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Trial Comparing Clopidogrel Plus Acetylsalicylic Acid (ASA) Versus ASA Alone in Subjects With Acute ST Elevation Myocardial Infarction (STEMI) Treated With Fibrinolytic Therapy</official_title>
